{"type":"message","id":"9f9dc7c6","parentId":"c484133b","timestamp":"2026-03-22T09:51:02.717Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Zach wants me to run a self-upgrade cycle. Let me think about what that means - probably updating skills, checking for new versions, refreshing my knowledge base, etc. Let me run through some self-maintenance tasks.\n\nI should:\n1. Check for skill updates via clawhub\n2. Review and update memory files\n3. Maybe do some housekeeping\n\nLet me start with checking what needs upgrading.","thinkingSignature":"3989507c63c10f40ac9a2cb79ad16eacb711897620c195c707af9f7b21319c10"},{"type":"text","text":"On it. Let me run through upgrades and cleanup.\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_x5gbiqa9hxds_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd C:/Users/Zwmar/.openclaw/workspace && git status"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_x5gbiqa9hxds_2","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"clawhub --version 2>$null; if ($LASTEXITCODE -ne 0) { npx clawhub --version }"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":43,"output":179,"cacheRead":12753,"cacheWrite":153,"totalTokens":13128,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774173055585}}
