{"type":"message","id":"cbde51ab","parentId":"c756f27c","timestamp":"2026-03-22T12:50:23.042Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Zach said \"go ahead\" - meaning I should proceed with setting up the Paperspace gateway. Let me work on this.\n\nFirst I need to understand the current Paperspace setup and what's already configured. Let me check the TOOLS.md and any existing Paperspace configuration.\n\nFrom TOOLS.md:\n- Remote GPU on Paperspace Gradient\n- A5000: 30GB VRAM\n- Sandbox: `~/.openclaw/sandbox/`\n- Zach said no Ollama — sandbox uses stateless compositional architecture instead\n\nSo the plan is:\n1. Spin up a Gradient notebook with vLLM\n2. Deploy a model (Qwen or similar)\n3. Get the endpoint + API key\n\n\n4. Wire it into the sandbox\n\nI should check if Paperspace CLI is available and look at what's already in the sandbox directory to see what I'm working with.","thinkingSignature":"6f6d75c7f5705b51206842b793766d5a098a6ec317f20ff2ce005e2ab790d72e"},{"type":"text","text":"On it. Let me check the Paperspace setup and sandbox state first.\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_d9vhpm24k9pr_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"pspace --version 2>&1; pspace status 2>&1 | head -20","timeout":15}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_d9vhpm24k9pr_2","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"ls -la C:/Users/Zwmar/.openclaw/sandbox/ 2>&1"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_d9vhpm24k9pr_3","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cat C:/Users/Zwmar/.openclaw/workspace/TOOLS.md | grep -A 20 \"Paperspace\""}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":43,"output":324,"cacheRead":1307,"cacheWrite":28706,"totalTokens":30380,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774183810884}}
